These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, tea
House: art-deco, cape-cod, colonial
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, biathlon, climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, rock, jazz
The people have 3 different hobbies: sudoku, singing, skydiving
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, blend, bongani
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the art-deco house is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the cape-cod house##2
8. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | tea     | milk      | fanta      |
| House          | cape-cod   | art-deco   | colonial       |
| Sport   | climbing | soccer | biathlon    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | electronic    | rock    |
| Hobby           | singing    | skydiving    | sudoku |
| Cigar     | blend  | bongani     | dannemann        |

