2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growsorchid is the person who growsorchid##1
4. the mechanic is the fan of folk##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the modern house is between the cottage house and the person traveling to hannover##2
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
8. the fan of folk is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
9. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| City          | hannover  | san-francisco    | marseilles   |
| House         | colonial | modern | cottage |
