2. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
3. the siglo-smoker is the accountant##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the teacher is on the right of the paramedic##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
8. the futuristic house is between the person who likes fuchsia and the dannemann-smoker##2
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta      | water     | mirinda      |
| Color          | fuchsia     | light-blue     | orange     |
| House         | art-deco      | futuristic | farmhouse    |
