.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, pomegranate, lime
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, indonesian, argentine
3 different games are played: go, whist, domino
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
City: san-francisco, liverpool, rome
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine, apricot
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes blue and the owner of the snake##2
3. the indonesian is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person playing whist##1
5. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating lime##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the argentine##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing go##1
8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food      | lime     | lettuce   | pomegranate      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | argentine  | nigerian  |
| Game   | go       | whist  | domino        |
| Pet           | snake       | rabbit   | guinea-pig |
| City         | liverpool      | rome | san-francisco   |
| Color     | aquamarine   | apricot     | blue |

 